quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,23,"Min dey mi tawii debbo no laamii …ìe, on debbo no okkaa kala huunde immorde e sabuuji doole laamu, himo jogii jullere laamu mawnde himo fewja e hoore mayre fiyakuuji yim…ìe makko …ìen."
  27,24,"Mi tawii oo debbo, mi tawii yim…ìe makko …ìen kadi hi…ìe sujjana naange ngen gaanin Alla Senii…óo Toowu…óo On, Seytaane labinani …ìe ko …ìe woni kon e muu…óum immorde e golle sirku ngun e geddi …óin, o martini …ìe gaayi Laawol Goongawol ngol, kam…ìe …ìe feewataa e maggol."
  27,25,"Seytaane labinani …ìe golle sirku ngun e geddi …óin; fii wata …ìe sujjan Alla Kanko tun, On yaltinoowo ko O suu…ói kon ka kammu immorde e to…ìo ngon, e ka leydi immorde e pu…ói …óin, hiMo Anndi golle …óe suu…óoton …óen, e …óe fe√±√±inton …óen, hay huunde e …óum suu…óanaaki Mo."
  27,26,"Alla, rewetee…óo e goonga alaa tanaa Makko, Jooma Arsi Mawki kin."
  27,27,"Sulaymaana (yo o his) maakani hud-huda: Aray men ndaara si a goongu e koo ko nodditi…óaa …óum, maa…óum si a wonu jeyaa…óo e fenu…ìe …ìen."
  27,28,"Sulaymaana winndi …ìatakuru, o jonnindu hud-huda, o wi'ani hud-huda: Yahidu e nduu …ìatakuru am werlo…óaa nde ka yim…ìe Saba'i jonnu…ìe ndu, pottito…óaa …ìe sera nokku ka nanataa ko …ìe jaabondita kon e fiyaake mayru."
  27,29,"Lam…óo on ja…ìi …ìatakuru ndun, o wi'i: Ko onon yo teddu…ìe, min dey …ìatakuru teddundu mawnundu werlaama ka am."
  27,30,"Ko woni e nder nduu …ìatakuru nulaandu immorde e Sulaymaana udditiraandu sabu "Innde Alla Huu…ìu…óo Yurmeende Heerii…óo Yurmeende":"
  27,31,"Wata on mawnintino, aree ka am hara ko on …óoftii…ìe jebbilanii…ìe ko mi noddi on kon e muu…óum immorde e Ngootimmbaaku Alla e accitugol ko wono…óon e mu'un kon immorde e sirkanngol Mo, nokku ka rewoton naange ngen wonndude e Makko."
  27,32,"Lam…óo on wi'i: Ko onon yo teddu…ìe e koohoo…ìe, …ìannginanee lam feere feewunde nden e fiyaake am on, mi wonaali √±aawoowo fiyaake haa tawde…óon e am, fe√±√±inon feere moo…óon nde e nder mu'un."
  27,33,"Teddu…ìe …ìen ka yim…ìe makko wi'i: Enen ko en jooma doole maw…óe, e jooma aalaaji hare dolnu…ói ka hare, feere nden ko ko fewju…óaawoo ndaaru ko hon…óum yamirtaa men haray menen ko men hattan…ìe e dow siinugol …óum."
  27,34,"Laamii…óo on wi'i: Pellet, lam…ìe …ìen si …ìe naatii e saare immorde e ca'e …óen …ìe bonniray nde sabu ko …ìe jokkata kon warugol e jattugol, …ìe wa…óa koohoo…ìe mayre e teddu…ìe mayre hoy…ìe …ìaawo ko …ìe wonunoo kon e muu…óum immorde e teddu- ngal e neema, ko wanonii lam…ìe …ìen gollirta tuma kala …ìe fooli yim…ìe saare; fii yo …ìe aawu mirin e kulol ka wonkiiji."
  27,35,"Awa min, mi nulay haa e jooma nduu …ìatakuru e yim…ìe makko …ìen neldaari, mi ndaara ko hon…óum nulaa…ìe …ìen ardata e muu…óum …ìaawo jonnugol ndii neldaari."